ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectAdele Louise Bisaillon ** leasehold interest in an unsurveyed parcel of land **
PrecisOrder authorizing ADELE LOUISE BISAILLON, an employee of the Government of Canada, to acquire through assignment of an existing lease, a leasehold interest in a surveyed parcel of land in the Northwest Territories.
